"title": "5057: rest, physical",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5057: rest, physical",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The need for physical rest is recognised in Scripture, and provision is made for ensuring that people are allowed time for rest.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ needed physical rest</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:6\">JHN 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:38\">MRK 4:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:31\">MRK 6:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:58\">LUK 9:58</a></p>\n<h2>The provision of rest</h2>\n<h3>The need for rest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:31\">MRK 6:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:2-Ps23:3\">PSA 23:2–23:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:1\">PRO 17:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:6\">ECC 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:30\">MAT 11:28–11:30</a></p>\n<h3>Provision of sleep for rest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:8\">PSA 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:2\">PSA 127:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:12\">ECC 5:12</a></p>\n<h3>Provision of a Sabbath-rest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:21\">EXO 34:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:27\">MRK 2:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:8-Exod20:11\">EXO 20:8–20:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:12-Deut5:15\">DEU 5:12–5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:15\">EXO 31:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:2\">EXO 35:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:3\">LEV 23:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:15\">NEH 13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:13-Isa58:14\">ISA 58:13–58:14</a></p>\n<h2>The purpose of rest</h2>\n<h3>To renew strength</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:5\">LAM 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:29-Isa40:31\">ISA 40:29–40:31</a></p>\n<h3>To know peace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:25-Matt6:34\">MAT 6:25–6:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:18-Job11:19\">JOB 11:18–11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:5\">PSA 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:8\">PSA 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:24\">PRO 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6-Phil4:7\">PHP 4:6–4:7</a></p>\n<h2>The character of rest</h2>\n<h3>The absence of war</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:23\">JOS 11:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh14:15\">JOS 14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:4\">1KI 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:9\">1CH 22:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:9-Ps46:10\">PSA 46:9–46:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:33\">PRO 1:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:3\">ISA 14:3</a></p>\n<h3>The absence of social strife</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:4\">ECC 10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:10\">1CO 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:11\">1TH 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:14\">HEB 12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:17-Jas3:18\">JAS 3:17–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>The absence of fear</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:37-Mark4:38\">MRK 4:37–4:38</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:24-Matt8:25\">MAT 8:24–8:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:23-Luke8:24\">LUK 8:23–8:24</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:11\">GEN 32:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:2\">PSA 127:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:4\">MIC 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:31\">MAT 6:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:29\">LUK 12:29</a></p>\n<h3>The absence of anxiety</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:7\">1PE 5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:25\">MAT 6:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6\">PHP 4:6</a></p>\n<h3>The presence of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:14\">EXO 33:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:27\">DEU 33:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28\">MAT 11:28</a></p>\n<h3>The experience of security</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:12\">DEU 33:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:23\">PRO 19:23</a></p>\n<h3>The experience of peace in death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:13\">REV 14:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:16\">DEU 31:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:13-Job3:17\">JOB 3:13–3:17</a></p>\n<h2>The destruction of rest</h2>\n<h3>By business</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:6\">PSA 39:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:40\">GEN 31:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:13\">ECC 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:23\">ECC 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:16\">ECC 8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:34\">LUK 21:34</a></p>\n<h3>By conflict</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:5\">2CO 7:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:5\">LAM 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:5\">2CO 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:27\">2CO 11:27</a></p>\n<h3>By grief</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer45:3\">JER 45:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:26\">JOB 3:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:4\">PSA 77:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:18\">DAN 6:18</a></p>\n<h3>By unconfessed guilt</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:3-Ps32:5\">PSA 32:3–32:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:12\">GEN 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:65-Deut28:67\">DEU 28:65–28:67</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:22\">ISA 48:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:20-Isa57:21\">ISA 57:20–57:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:11\">REV 14:11</a></p>\n<h3>By sickness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:17\">JOB 30:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:4-Job7:5\">JOB 7:4–7:5</a></p>",
